snippet.title: Aladdin Cinematic 4
snippet.description: Animated video game cinematic produced in 1997 by Heart of Texas Productions (Austin, TX) for an un-released Disney Interactive title, "Aladdin and the Fate of Agrabbah".  Animation by Keith Wilson.
